WJMQ 92.3 FM
FROG 92.3 HIT COUNTRY 
Frog 92.3 features new country music hits, with a focus on upbeat and popular tracks from current artists. The format also includes some crossover hits from other genres, such as pop and rock. This format is popular among audiences who enjoy mainstream country music.
Example artists include Luke Bryan, Blake Shelton, Carrie Underwood, and Miranda Lambert. Example songs include "Good Time" by Niko Moon, "One Margarita" by Luke Bryan, and "Wine, Beer, Whiskey" by Little Big Town.
Feature Programming: Green Bay Packer Football, High School Sports, Polka Show Sunday Nights, Local News and Sports, Weather.
Over the Air Coverage: Waupaca, Shawano, and Outagamie Counties.
